      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Historic Downtown</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">The Woodlands</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Stirling Chase</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Dunedin Isles</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Skinner Bayou</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Marina District</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Caladesi</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Palm Harbor</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Clearwater</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Oldsmar</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Safety Harbor</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Tarpon Springs</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Curlew</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Honeymoon Island</span>
      <span class="scard px-4 py-3 text-center" style="font-size:.9rem;font-weight:600">Countryside</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-12"><p class="sl gt mb-3">Common Questions</p><h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em">DUNEDIN ROOFING FAQ</h2></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">How much does a roof replacement cost in Dunedin?<svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">A Dunedin roof replacement typically costs $8,000 to $24,000+ depending on size, pitch, material, and structural condition. Older bungalows near downtown and newer homes in outlying areas vary in pricing. Call <a href="tel:8135957663" class="call-tracking-number" style="color:#3B9FD9;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">(813) 595-7663</a> for a free estimate.</div></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">What roofing material works best for Dunedin homes?<svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Dunedin's Gulf-side location brings salt air, UV exposure, and storm winds. Shingles with 130+ MPH ratings are most popular. Metal reflects heat and resists salt corrosion for 40–60 years. Tile offers a classic look. We install all three and help you choose the best option for your home.</div></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">Does Happy Roof handle City of Dunedin permits?<svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes. We handle all permit applications and inspections with the City of Dunedin and Pinellas County. You never visit a government office - we manage everything from application to final sign-off.</div></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">How long does a Dunedin roof replacement take?<svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Most Dunedin shingle roofs are completed in 1 to 3 days. Metal takes 3 to 5 days, tile 5 to 7 days. We schedule around weather and keep you informed. Full cleanup and debris removal is included.</div></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">Is Happy Roof licensed to work in Dunedin?<svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes. Happy Roof LLC holds Florida License #CCC1337380, authorizing roofing work throughout Florida including Dunedin and all of Pinellas County. Full general liability and workers' compensation insurance carried.</div></div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-grad relative overflow-hidden py-20"><div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 text-center"><h2 class="font-display font-black tracking-tightest mb-4" style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4.5rem);line-height:.92;letter-spacing:-.01em">READY TO GET STARTED<span style="color:#F0C040">?</span></h2><p style="color:rgba(255,248,240,.85);font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:2rem">Call us or request a free estimate online - we respond within 24 hours.</p><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center"><a href="/contact" class="btn-t" style="font-size:1.15rem;padding:1rem 2.5rem">Get My Free Estimate <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg></a><a href="tel:8135957663" class="btn-o call-tracking-number" style="font-size:1.05rem;padding:1rem 2.5rem">Call Now - No Obligation</a></div></div></section>

